Greece Must Be ‘Smaller, Smarter’ State, Venizelos Says

-- B y   P a u l   T u g w e l l   a n d   E l e n i   C h r e p a
-- 
2011-09-19T07:33:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/greece-must-be-smaller-smarter-state-venizelos-says.html
Greek Finance Minister Evangelos Venizelos said the state had to become “smaller and smarter”
and that the focus on the 2012 budget would be on spending cuts.
He spoke at a conference in  Athens  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
